TypeSignature.Value: .class public auto ansi sealed PageMediaSizeName extends System.Enum

Docs.summary: Specifies the page size or roll width of the paper or other print media.

remarks.format: ## Remarks This enumeration is used to provide values for the <xref:System.Printing.PageMediaSize.PageMediaSizeName%2A> property. The <xref:System.Printing.PageMediaSize> class, in turn, is used to provide values for the <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.PageMediaSizeCapability%2A> property where it specifies the various page sizes a printer can use, and the <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket.PageMediaSize%2A> property, where it instructs a printer which page size to use.
